column5: I heard the IT crowd was funny. Is that on Netflix?
Thank you for your suggestions. A magnifying glass would work wonders to crush my fear of little spaces. 😃
I’ve never started a PBN because you I fear all those little spaces & not being able to shade.
Beautiful!!  Do you have a link to a pattern?
I’m sorry you feel so down. DM me if you want to chat.
I followed you on IG. Love what you’re doing. 💕
I love gardein. Never been disappointed. 😋
Just the contrast between the two pictures makes me want to cry 😢 Devastating. I’m so sorry.
Why are the murder mitts highlighted in red as they push down?
Sounds like a good setup & one happy Jelly Bean 😃

I would be worried too. Is she planning on taking her meds with her?  Maybe ask if you could come along?  You have time to try to talk her out of it.  Sending you positive thoughts. I sincerely hope everything turns out ok.
Makes a lot of sense. I saved it.
Yw. Hope you feel better & sweet dreams 💫
You can pm me if you like. I’ll try to help. I’ll be up for a bit.
It ended too soon. I wanted to see the hooman come in.
I can almost hear her purring 💕
I’ve seen that video too. The seal was actually pushing dead penguins into the divers camera desperately trying to feed this helpless human.
I can’t believe it has been 28 years🎶
Do you use pencils or markers?
Love the way you colored the letters 🌈
It looks kind of like the sorting hat in Harry Potter.
Poor thing. Just running the fence of the enclosure.
Thank you for rescuing them 💕 Do they have a pond to swim around in?
Love the shading on the dress & leaves 🌈
Oh my goodness 😃 Love the blue lightning coming from its mouth!
So sorry for your loss. Hope you can take refuge with your memories. 💕
I’m not crying you are. I feel your loss😢
I love the name of your new show & wish you well 💫
What a cute little face!!!!  So happy that Maxwell is safe.
Awwwwwwwww, I just joined. Thanks for trying. See you on YouTube.
Awwwwwww, look at those eyes!!!!  I just can’t cope 💕
You were really lucky to have all those wonderful memories of your Dad ❤️
Is that a scar?  Poor baby!  But beautiful smile 😃
Yes & she’ll be over the rainbow bridge waiting for you 💕
Looks like something out of a storybook ✨
